Arch Config Live ISO

Repository: /opt/arch-linux-config
Installer:  archcfg-install

This live ISO is only the installer environment. The installed system is still
created by install.sh from the repository.

UEFI is required for the installer target.

Common VM command:
  archcfg-install --vm --disk /dev/sda --profile virtualbox

Repeated disposable VM test:
  archcfg-install --vm --disk /dev/sda --profile virtualbox --yes
